race.description: John Loftus Happy 90Th Birthday Mdn Hcp
race.comment: PENROSE (6) sets the standard presenting fitter off a narrow defeat at Albury over 900m where she led. Draws perfectly and is sure to take plenty of catching. Wary of EXTRIO (7), who has switched to the local Pepper yard on a 150-day return. Trialled like a cracker before disappointing as a $1.90F at Newcastle and was immediately tipped out. Has an in-form rider booked and expect her to be wound right up for 'cup-day'. SKIBIDI (2) is a local on debut and has trialled well enough. Has the handy 2kg claim and has to be considered. FLYING CORSAIR (1) is another local on debut. Was close up in his latest Canberra trial and has the inside barrier. Heywood's engagement interests.
